Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:18:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,脸色不断变换 却始终魅力无限
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:04.49,dingbu,,0,0,0,,בכל פינה
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,存在于城市的每个角落里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:10.57,dingbu,,0,0,0,,You and I have made this far, oh, baby on our won
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你我已走到这一地步 噢宝贝 我们赢得了胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:16.24,dingbu,,0,0,0,,We've been rowing boat as lovers 'till we lost the oar
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们如恋人般划着轻舟 直到我们失去了桨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:20.92,dingbu,,0,0,0,,Letting stars and rain to fall on us, and we hoped
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(624,573.333)}让星星和雨点打在我们身上 然后我们许下愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:27.98,dingbu,,0,0,0,,that the flowers and the sun will cherish us forever
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(560,576)}希望花朵和暖阳将会永远珍爱我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:33.08,dingbu,,0,0,0,,You and I have made a perfect pair to live along
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(600,546.667)}你和我本已珠联璧合 一起生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:38.67,dingbu,,0,0,0,,Trying too hard not to realize we can't live for long
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(618.666,581.333)}却难以意识到 这样无法长久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:43.29,dingbu,,0,0,0,,Only now it's clear enough for us to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(600,560)}只有现在我们才清楚地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是 血界战线 赫尔沙雷姆兹·罗特的居民 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可以看到的东西一样 应该是最好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我的音乐怎么说呢 就是像这样的感觉来制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,像是身临其境这个世界一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是能够有这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,广告过后 那支实力乐队终于出场啦
